{"id":558374,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/文三娃-上帝抛弃了那个吃饱饭的人/","date":"2017-05-07T05:15:28Z","modified":"2017-05-07T05:15:28Z","title":"文三娃 | 上帝抛弃了那个吃饱饭的人","content":"<p>帝都昌平警方在抓嫖行动中致人死亡案之博弈，在2016平安夜前一天，以当值五警不诉收官。</p>\n<p>棋局已定，棋理哗然。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://news.sina.com.cn/s/2016-12-24/doc-ifxyxqsk6515501.shtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">检方通告耐人寻味，详细描述了警务人员在制服过程中使用各种暴力手段导致被约束人“体位发生变化”，死因描述中称“因执法过程中的外力作用和剧烈活动以及体位变化等因素有关”；违规安排（辅警）独立押送；辅警（保安员）周晶对被约束人有辱骂行为；被约束人身体出现异常时未进行现场急救、紧急呼救和送医抢救；事后编造事实、隐瞒真相、妨碍侦查。</a></p>\n<p>如果这段话能够出现在法庭，等待着几位被告的，有可能是“数罪并罚”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/1327554655.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558375\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/1327554655.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/1327554655.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/1327554655-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/1327554655-768x433.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>通告话锋一转，因犯罪情节轻微，“依法作出不起诉处理”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35g9icoj30hs0emq5h.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558376\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35g9icoj30hs0emq5h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35g9icoj30hs0emq5h.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35g9icoj30hs0emq5h-300x247.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>检方的潜台词或是：案情侦查我已履职，最后决定我不背锅。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xm2xfj30go0m8q42.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558377\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xm2xfj30go0m8q42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xm2xfj30go0m8q42.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xm2xfj30go0m8q42-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xmxzxj30qo0zkmyk.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558379\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xw1doj30go0m8abl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xw1doj30go0m8abl.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xw1doj30go0m8abl-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xmxzxj30qo0zkmyk.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558378\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xmxzxj30qo0zkmyk.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xmxzxj30qo0zkmyk.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xmxzxj30qo0zkmyk-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc35xmxzxj30qo0zkmyk-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>警界的情绪亦很微妙。我所在的某微信群有十几位警队朋友，平时谈笑风生，此刻均保持了沉默。</p>\n<p>网友十年砍柴的这段点评，我认为是基本准确的，经砍兄同意转发。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36foe6sj30hs09sae8.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558380\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36foe6sj30hs09sae8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"303\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36foe6sj30hs09sae8.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36foe6sj30hs09sae8-300x165.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而就在警队进入静默期，著名公知、外围警务工作者胡杨麟先生（字可岩，又名谷雨航）又一次冷不丁从斜刺杀出，以一己之力扩大涉警舆情。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36tdd6lj30hs0iztfr.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558381\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36tdd6lj30hs0iztfr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"587\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36tdd6lj30hs0iztfr.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc36tdd6lj30hs0iztfr-281x300.jpg 281w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>胡先生有个嗜好，在热点事件中，坚持把警队不太方便说的细节或者不太好公开表达的情绪转赠给大众。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558384\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc37pddi4j30hs0vkmzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"976\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc37pddi4j30hs0vkmzq.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc37pddi4j30hs0vkmzq-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc37pddi4j30hs0vkmzq-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3avrks4j30x713lwi5.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558382\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3avrks4j30x713lwi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3avrks4j30x713lwi5.jpg 1195w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3avrks4j30x713lwi5-252x300.jpg 252w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3avrks4j30x713lwi5-768x916.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3avrks4j30x713lwi5-859x1024.jpg 859w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3bcmdy1j30hs0vkn1h.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558385\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3bcmdy1j30hs0vkn1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"976\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3bcmdy1j30hs0vkn1h.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3bcmdy1j30hs0vkn1h-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3bcmdy1j30hs0vkn1h-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>回到涉嫖致死案，警界、检界、律界、媒界传递出的信息与情绪，纵横交错，剪不断，理还乱。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3cru59kj30hs0vk43s.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-558386\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3cru59kj30hs0vk43s.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"976\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3cru59kj30hs0vk43s.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3cru59kj30hs0vk43s-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/006DvdLsly1ffc3cru59kj30hs0vk43s-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>​嗟乎！</p>\n<p>这个丙申耶诞节并不 merry ,上帝抛弃了那个吃饱饭的人。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[19200,18974,28824,18243,26167,14567,28627,23689,31076,31492]}